<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy - Energy Monitoring System</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 min-h-screen text-gray-800">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto p-6">
    <div class="bg-white/95 rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last Updated: January 15, 2024</p>

      <section class="space-y-4 leading-7">
        <p><strong>Your Privacy Matters:</strong> We are committed to protecting your personal information.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>Account information, usage analytics, and energy monitoring data.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">2. How We Use Data</h2>
        <p>To provide and improve service, support users, and generate energy insights.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">3. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We apply technical and organizational controls to protect your data.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">4. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data.</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">5. Contact</h2>
        <p>Email: privacy@energymonitor.com</p>
      </section>

      <a href="/auth/register" class="inline-flex mt-8 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 text-white hover:bg-indigo-700">
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left mr-2 mt-1"></i> Back to Registration
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
